OL,3,CMore than 10% of Scottish prisoners
OL,4,Creleased early already back in jail
OL,6,FMore than 10% of criminals who were
OL,7,Freleased early from Scottish prisons
OL,8,Fhave already been returned to jail.
OL,10,FFigures from the Scottish Prison
OL,11,FService showed 57 out of the 477
OL,12,Fprisoners released early were returned
OL,13,Fto custody.
OL,15,FThe figure includes those charged and
OL,16,Fre-convicted of a crime, remanded and
OL,17,Fawaiting trial, and those who have
OL,18,Fbeen released from remand after being
OL,19,Fcharged.
