OL,3,CMore than 10% of Scottish prisoners
OL,4,Creleased early already back in jail
OL,6,FA Scottish Prison Service spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid the Emergency Early Release (EER)
OL,8,Fprogramme had prioritised the "safety
OL,9,Fand wellbeing of those in our care,
OL,10,Fvictims, and the communities we serve."
OL,12,FThey said the EER had provided "much
OL,13,Fneeded respite to our establishments"
OL,14,Fbut it was only ever a temporary
OL,15,Fmeasure and "In recent months, our
OL,16,Fpopulation has risen sharply once
OL,17,Fmore."
