OL,3,CMore than 10% of Scottish prisoners
OL,4,Creleased early already back in jail
OL,6,FThe spokesperson added: "This
OL,7,Fcontinues to have a significant impact
OL,8,Fon our staff and the time available to
OL,9,Fthem to do the important work in
OL,10,Fsupporting people, building
OL,11,Frelationships, turning lives around,
OL,12,Freducing the risk of reoffending, and
OL,13,Fcreating a safer Scotland for all."
OL,15,FThe Scottish EER happened over the
OL,16,Fsummer, with England and Wales
OL,17,Freleasing around 1,700 prisoners in a
OL,18,Fsimilar scheme in mid-September.
