OL,3,CMore than 10% of Scottish prisoners
OL,4,Creleased early already back in jail
OL,6,FA separate report published by the
OL,7,FScottish Government puts the projected
OL,8,Fprison population at between 7,750 and
OL,9,F9,250 at the beginning of next year,
OL,10,Fwith it being "likely" there will be
OL,11,Fan increase in numbers between August
OL,12,Fof this year and January.
OL,14,FPrisons have been struggling under the
OL,15,Fweight of high populations in recent
OL,16,Fyears, with 8,274 people in custody as
OL,17,Fof September 27.
